OL,6,FAn ITV News investigation has been
OL,7,Funcovering the medical scandal of the
OL,8,Fdrug DES and the ongoing fight for
OL,9,Fjustice, as Social Affairs
OL,10,FCorrespondent Sarah Corker and Senior
OL,11,FProducer Lottie Kilraine report
OL,13,FAn ITV News investigation has found
OL,14,Fshocking new evidence that health
OL,15,Fauthorities failed to ban a dangerous
OL,16,Fpregnancy drug prescribed on the NHS,
OL,17,Fdespite mounting evidence of its links
OL,18,Fto cancer.
