OL,6,FThe anti-miscarriage drug
OL,7,FDiethlystilbestrol, commonly known as
OL,8,FDES, was given to hundreds of
OL,9,Fthousands of women between the 1950s
OL,10,Fand 1980s, some of whom have developed
OL,11,Frare cancers and had the harm "passed
OL,12,Fdown generations".
OL,14,FThe Health Secretary has now admitted
OL,15,Fthat the "state failed" to take
OL,16,Fregulatory action and said he was
OL,17,Fexploring what "effective redress and
OL,18,Fremedy" could look like.
