OL,6,F"This in itself was very traumatic for
OL,7,Fme as I was a 15-year-old child
OL,8,Fgrieving for my mother," Michelle told
OL,9,FITV Tonight. "I passed out with the
OL,10,Fpain and was recalled to be examined
OL,11,Funder anaesthetic."
OL,13,FFor years the sisters were examined
OL,14,Fevery six months, then annually, as
