OL,6,FMedicines watchdog misled public over
OL,7,FDES
OL,9,FThe UK medicines regulator, the MHRA
OL,10,Fhad claimed that doctors were advised
OL,11,Fto stop using DES in 1973, but
OL,12,Ffollowing our reporting they have now
OL,13,Ffor the first time admitted that never
OL,14,Fhappened and apologised for
OL,15,F"inaccurate" statements.
OL,17,FDozens of women have contacted ITV
OL,18,FNews saying they'd been given DES on
OL,19,Fthe NHS nearly a decade after 1973.
