OL,6,FOur team then scoured through hundreds
OL,7,Fof pages of public health records at
OL,8,Fthe National Archives and British
OL,9,FLibrary.
OL,11,FWe found no evidence that regulatory
OL,12,Faction was ever taken to withdraw the
OL,13,Fdrug, and in fact that doctors
OL,14,Fdownplayed the risks.
OL,16,FThe MHRA has now apologised for "this
OL,17,Ferror and for any distress caused to
OL,18,Fpatients and the public".
